cial%20Investigation%20Team%20took%20Martin%20to%20his%20residence%20at%20Athani%20near%20Aluva%20here%2C%20where%20the%20explosive%20devices%20were%20suspected%20to%20have%20been%20assembled%2C%20in%20pursuit%20of%20crucial%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20several%20hours%2C%20Martin%20provided%20a%20detailed%20account%20of%20the%20construction%20process%2C%20using%20the%20materials%20he%20claimed%20to%20have%20used%20in%20the%20explosion%20that%20claimed%20three%20lives%20and%20left%20over%2050%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20Martin%20surrendered%20before%20the%20police%20on%20Sunday%2C%20he%20had%20produced%20bills%20for%20the%20purchased%20materials%2C%20further%20strengthening%20the%20case%20against%20him%2C%20according%20to%20a%20senior%20police%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBills%20for%20petrol%20purchases%20linked%20to%20the%20creation%20of%20the%20explosive%20were%20among%20the%20documents%20he%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDescribed%20as%20a%20person%20of%20%26quot%3Bexceptional%20intelligence%20and%20diligence%26quot%3B%2C%20Martin's%20decision%20to%20relinquish%20a%20high-paying%20overseas%20position%20for%20such%20a%20shocking%20act%20has%20confounded%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20proficiency%20in%20electronics%20was%20taken%20note%20of%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMartin%2C%20wearing%20a%20face-covering%20mask%2C%20was%20presented%20before%20the%20court%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20application%20is%20set%20to%20be%20submitted%20for%20a%20test%20identification%20parade%20at%20the%20Chief%20Judicial%20Magistrate%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20a%20procedural%20step%20in%20the%20legal%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20offered%20legal%20assistance%20multiple%20times%20by%20the%20court%2C%20Martin%20insisted%20on%20representing%20himself.%20He%20stated%20clearly%20that%20this%20is%20his%20choice%2C%20dispelling%20any%20notions%20of%20financial%20difficulties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBesi