kistan%20pacer%20Shaheen%20Shah%20Afridi%20led%20the%20pace%20attack%20brilliantly%20to%20bowl%20out%20Bangladesh%20for%20a%20paltry%20204%20before%20they%20cantered%20home%20in%2032.3%20overs%20to%20hugely%20boost%20their%20net%20run-rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20win%20in%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20gives%20you%20confidence.%20We%20also%20waited%20for%20this%20win%2C%26quot%3B%20Zaman%20said%20at%20the%20post-match%20media%20interaction.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20now%20started%20to%20find%20our%20rhythm.%20Against%20South%20Africa%2C%20we%20made%20comebacks%20while%20batting%20as%20well%20as%20bowling.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20getting%20our%20combinations%20right.%20I've%20been%20part%20of%20this%20dressing%20room%20for%20eight%20years%20now%2C%20it%20will%20improve%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMaking%20a%20comeback%20after%20five%20matches%2C%20Fakhar%20struck%20a%2074-ball%2081%20and%20laid%20the%20foundation%20with%20Abdullah%20Shafique%20(68)%20in%20a%20128-run%20opening%20stand.%20It%20made%20it%20a%20straightforward%20chase%20for%20Pakistan%20as%20they%20looked%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20seal%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20situation%20we%20are%20in%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20we%20were%20looking%20to%20chase%20it%20in%2029-30%20overs.%20Ifs%20and%20buts%20will%20be%20there%2C%20but%20our%20target%20is%20semifinal%20and%20we%20will%20try%20for%20that%20only%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20win%20saw%20Pakistan%20snap%20their%20four-match%20losing%20streak%20and%20move%20past%20Afghanistan%20into%20fifth%20place%20on%20net%20run-rate%20with%20six%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20now%20have%20to%20win%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20England%20in%20their%20last%20two%20games%20to%20get%20to%2010%20points%20and%20hope%20that%20at%20least%20one%20of%20New%20Zealand%20or%20Australia%20slip%20in%20the%20points%20table%20losing%20two%20or%20more%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDown%20with%20a%20niggle%2C%20Zaman%20had%20to%20sit%20out%20for%20five%20matches%20after%20their%20World%20Cup%20opener%20against%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20injury%20was%20not%20that%20severe%20and%20I%20had%20to%20sit%20out%20for%20precaution.%20If%20team%20needed%20me%2C%20I%20would%20have%20played.%20Today%20I%20got%20a%20chance%2C%20and%20did%20my%20best%20in%20team's%20win.%26quot%3B%20Zaman%20said%20he's%20hungry%20for%20more%20such%20knocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20I'm%20playing%20at%20the%20nets%20I've%20a%20fair%20idea%20that%20the%20ball%20is%20coming%20well%20on%20bat.%20On%20Indian%20wickets%2C%20the%20key%20is%20to%20hang%20around%20for%20three-four%20overs%20and%20then%20it%20becomes%20easy%20to%20score%20runs.%20The%20boundaries%20are%20also%20short.%20I%20want%20to%20perform%20similarly%20in%20next%20matches%2C%20so%20that%20we%20make%20semis.%26quot%3B%20He%20further%20said%20the%20bowlers%20have%20now%20aced%20the%20conditions%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20spend%20time%20in%20the%20middle%20you%20get%20an%20idea%2C%20initially%20our%20pacers%20were%20trying%20for%20more%20but%20the%20key%20here%20is%20accuracy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Pakistan's%20loss%20against%20India%20still%20hurt%20them%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20an%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20match%20is%20a%20very%20big%20deal.%20If%20I%20say%20it%20doesn't%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20I%20would%20be%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20all%20the%20players%20are%20professional%20and%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20cricket.%20Even%20against%20India%2C%20they%20have%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20matches.%20So%2C%20you%20can't%20say%20anything%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698812280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fgh02ju18_fakhar-zaman_625x300_01_November_23.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdefeat-against-india-hurt-pakistan-star-fakhar-zaman-opens-up-on-world-cup-setback-4532973%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Asked%20if%20Pakistan's%20loss%20against%20India%20still%20hurt%20them%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20an%20India%20and%20Pakistan%20match%20is%20a%20very%20big%20deal.%20If%20I%20say%20it%20doesn't%20make%20a%20difference%2C%20I%20would%20be%20wrong.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A83%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdefeat-against-india-hurt-pakistan-star-fakhar-zaman-opens-up-on-world-cup-setback-4532973%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdefeat-against-india-hurt-pakistan-star-fakhar-zaman-opens-up-on-world-cup-setback-4532973%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fdefeat-against-india-hurt-pakistan-star-fakhar-zaman-opens-up-on-world-cup-setback-4532973%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Chawls%20Made%20Mumbai%20%26quot%3BCity%20Of%20Dreams%26quot%3B%2C%20To%20Be%20Replaced%20By%20Skyscrapers%20Soon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20the%20chawls%20of%20Mumbai%20have%20acted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20most%20important%20forms%20of%20affordable%20housing.%20Large%20tenement%20complexes%20built%20during%20Mumbai's%20industrial%20boom%20from%20the%201850s%20through%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%2020th%20century%2C%20chawls%20once%20housed%20workers%20from%20the%20sprawling%20ports%20and%20textile%20mills%20of%20what%20was%20then%20called%20Bombay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20city%20bounded%20by%20water%20on%20three%20sides%20where%20land%20has%20long%20been%20scarce%2C%20these%20hulking%20complexes%20always%20presented%20challenging%20conditions%2C%20built%20to%20three%20floors%20or%20more%20to%20conserve%20valuable%20land%20and%20typically%20housing%20entire%20families%20in%20just%20a%20single%20room%20without%20private%20washing%20facilities.%20The%20chawls%20nonetheless%20offered%20generations%20of%20low-income%20arrivals%20in%20Mumbai%20a%20foothold%20in%20India's%20%26quot%3Bcity%20of%20dreams%26quot%3B%20and%20succeeded%20in%20becoming%20hives%20of%20community%20activity%20while%20offering%20homes%20that%20were%20close%20to%20workplaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20hundreds%20of%20chawls%20remain%2C%20housing%20many%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20residents%2C%20they%20are%20due%20to%20be%20swept%20away%20and%20replaced%20by%20high-rise%20residential%20towers%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20ambitious%20urban%20renewal%20plans%20the%20city%20has%20ever%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20chawls'%20upcoming%20demolition%20nonetheless%20signals%20the%20progress%20of%20two%20transformative%20trends%3A%20the%20disappearance%20of%20affordable%20housing%20from%20Mumbai's%20downtown%2C%20where%20chawls%20are%20overwhelmingly%20concentrated%2C%20and%20the%20end%20of%20its%20tradition%20of%20mingling%20the%20rich%20and%20poor%20in%20the%20same%20tight-knit%20neighborhoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20change%20may%20be%20striking%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20necessarily%20surprising.%20While%20their%20units%20are%20currently%20rented%20out%20at%20prices%20fixed%20by%20the%20state%20-%20often%20as%20little%20as%20the%20local%20equivalent%20to%20%241%20a%20month%20per%20unit%20in%20areas%20-%20the%20chawls%20stand%20on%20some%20of%20what%20is%20India's%20most%20valuable%20real%20estate%2C%20areas%20where%20even%20purpose-built%2C%20low-cost%20housing%20units%20cost%20on%20average%20%24400%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20of%20Mumbai's%20chawls%20tells%20a%20story%20whose%20outline%20is%20common%20to%20many%20megacities.%20The%20buildings%20sprang%20up%20during%20the%20British%20Raj%2C%20a%20time%20when%20new%20urban%20jobs%20were%20luring%20people%20in%20their%20thousands%20away%20from%20the%20countryside%20for%20work%20in%20textiles%20or%20as%20dockworkers%20in%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20ports%20in%20Britain's%20global%20empire.%20The%20growth%20of%20chawls%20can%20be%20thought%20of%20almost%20as%20synonymous%20with%20the%20expansion%20of%20the%20city.%20Before%20Bombay%20became%20a%20key%20harbor%20for%20trade%20and%20the%20British%20navy%2C%20the%20region%20was%20inhabited%20by%20small%20fishing%20communities.%20This%20transformation%20was%20powered%20partly%20by%20events%20in%20North%20America%2C%20as%20textile%20manufacturing%20boomed%20when%20the%20US%20Civil%20War%20cut%20off%20transatlantic%20cotton%20exports%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20boom%20fueled%20a%20desperate%20need%20for%20cheap%20housing%2C%20and%20chawls%20were%20a%20common%20answer.%20Typically%20built%20around%20a%20central%20courtyard%2C%20the%20chawls%20grouped%20rooms%20around%20a%20corridor%2C%20divided%20into%20either%20single%20or%20double%20room%20units%2C%20with%20bathrooms%20usually%20shared%20between%20the%20residents%20of%20each%20floor.%20This%20arrangement%20would%20perhaps%20have%20been%20ample%20with%20one%20or%20two%20workers%20per%20unit.%20In%20practice%2C%20this%20was%20never%20how%20they%20were%20used%20in%20India%2C%20where%20multiple%20generations%20-%20uncles%2C%20aunts%2C%20grandparents%20and%20cousins%20-%20shared%20space.%20For%20families%20arriving%20from%20the%20countryside%2C%20where%20they%20spread%20out%20across%20larger%20courtyard%20houses%2C%20the%20chawl%20apartments%20were%20an%20abrupt%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20chawls%20still%20offered%20(and%20continue%20to%20offer)%20benefits.%20Their%20density%20and%20grouping%20around%20courtyards%20-%20which%20still%20today%20continue%20to%20be%20the%20focus%20of%20activities%20like%20community%20sports%2C%20religious%20festivals%20and%20weddings%20-%20helped%20to%20generate%20camaraderie%20and%20community%20spirit%20between%20households.%20This%20spirit%20of%20sharing%20is%20underlined%20by%20regional%20community%20ties%20within%20chawls%2C%20as%20newly%20arrived%20families%20usually%20preferred%20to%20live%20with%20their%20own%20kind%2C%20along%20regional%2C%20linguistic%2C%20religious%20and%20caste%20lines.%20Most%20every%20community%20present%20in%20the%20city%20would%20have%20its%20own%20set%20of%20chawls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20community%20bonds%20have%20helped%20transform%20chawls%20into%20places%20where%20much%20space%20sits%20in%20a%20grey%20area%20between%20the%20public%20and%20the%20private.%20For%20low-income%20families%20in%20an%20expensive%20city%2C%20they%20offer%20a%20semblance%20of%20a%20safety%20net%20that%20the%20state%20doesn't%20provide.%20The%20solidarity%20they%20generate%20is%20especially%20helpful%20for%20those%20needing%20help%20with%20child-care%20or%20in%20creating%20opportunities%20to%20socialize%20for%20older%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20the%20architecture%20of%20the%20chawl%20provides%20in-between%20spaces%20between%20the%20house%20and%20the%20street%2C%20which%20are%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Prasad%20Shetty%2C%20co-founder%20and%20professor%20at%20School%20of%20Environment%20%26amp%3B%20Architecture%20in%20Mumbai.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20described%20it%20as%20an%20architecture%20of%20care.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETake%20for%20example%2C%20the%20BDD%20chawls%20in%20central%20Mumbai%20between%20the%20skyscrapers%20of%20Prabhadevi%20and%20Lower%20Parel.%20Built%20by%20the%20municipal%20government%20about%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20this%20area%20is%20inhabited%20by%20a%20large%20number%20of%20Buddhist%20followers%20of%20B.%20R.%20Ambedkar%2C%20an%20icon%20of%20caste%20consciousness%20and%20struggle%20in%20India%20whose%20likeness%20is%20found%20in%20shrines%20and%20painted%20on%20walls%20across%20the%20neighborhood.%20Despite%20this%20concentration%2C%20the%20area%20is%20not%20religiously%20or%20politically%20homogenous.%20Also%20represented%20here%20is%20the%20Maratha%20community%2C%20who%20hail%20from%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20vast%20state%20to%20which%20Mumbai%20is%20the%20capital.%20The%20community's%20votes%20make%20the%20area%20a%20stronghold%20for%20the%20right-wing%20regional%20Shiv%20Sena%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECramped%20houses%20also%20likely%20encouraged%20residents%20to%20stay%20outside%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%20whether%20at%20work%20or%20at%20the%20movies.%20The%20development%20of%20a%20passionate%20cinephile%20culture%20helped%20make%20Mumbai's%20Bollywood%20the%20center%20of%20the%20world's%20most-watched%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20houses%20were%20so%20small%2C%20cinemas%20and%20affordable%20food%20halls%20became%20really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rupali%20Gupte%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Mumbai's%20School%20of%20Environment%20%26amp%3B%20Architecture.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20this%20sense%20of%20the%20city%20as%20a%20whole%20becoming%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EArchitecturally%2C%20while%20most%20chawls'%20construction%20was%20plain%2C%20it%20was%20done%20thoughtfully.%20Early%20ones%20close%20to%20the%20city's%20dockyards%20have%20sloping%20roofs%20to%20fend%20off%20monsoonal%20rains%20that%20soak%20the%20city%20from%20June%20to%20October.%20Verandas%20help%20to%20protect%20interiors%20from%20rain%20and%20sun%20while%20ensuring%20good%20ventilation%20during%20humid%20summers.%20Earlier%20chawls%20built%20of%20wood%2C%20stone%20and%20brick%20helped%20create%20a%20more%20breathable%20fabric%20for%20each%20building.%20Residents%20also%20adapted%20other%20habits%20from%20older%20architecture%2C%20making%20up%20for%20the%20absence%20of%20substantial%20open%20or%20part-roofed%20spaces%20of%20traditional%20Konkan%20houses%20by%20using%20courtyards%2C%20balconies%20and%20verandas%20for%20daily%20activities%20and%20-%20with%20space%20at%20a%20premium%20-%20even%20sleeping.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20chawls%20lost%20many%20of%20these%20attributes.%20By%20the%201920s%2C%20they%20were%20increasingly%20built%20in%20configurations%20that%20loosely%20echoed%20the%20terraced%20houses%20inhabited%20by%20British%20industrial%20workers%2C%20albeit%20at%20much%20higher%20densities.%20Instead%20of%20being%20focused%20around%20courtyards%20that%20echoed%20traditional%20homes%20in%20rural%20India%2C%20these%20later%20chawls%20lined%20up%20rows%20of%20single%20aspect%20rooms%20that%20bore%20a%20loose%20(and%20possibly%20not%20coincidental)%20relationship%20to%20the%20back-to-back%20houses%20found%20earlier%20in%20the%20industrial%20cities%20of%20Britain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMumbai's%20chawls%20are%20long%20past%20their%20heyday.%20With%20the%20disappearance%20of%20much%20of%20the%20industry%20in%20which%20their%20original%20residents%20were%20employed%2C%20their%20condition%20has%20deteriorated%20and%20their%20crumbling%20exteriors%20may%20even%20be%20potentially%20unsafe.%20As%20these%20buildings%20now%20stand%20on%20land%20that%20is%20some%20of%20the%20most%20expensive%20per%20square%20foot%20in%20the%20world%2C%20redevelopment%20has%20become%20perhaps%20inevitable.%20And%20sure%20enough%2C%20a%20plan%20is%20now%20underway%20to%20replace%20the%20chawls%20with%20residential%20skyscrapers%2C%20a%20project%20that%20(after%20the%20proposed%20redevelopment%20of%20the%20Dharavi%20slums)%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20ambitious%20so-called%20urban%20renewal%20project%20in%20India%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government's%20blueprint%20for%20the%20area%20is%20to%20duplicate%20what%20its%20slum%20rehabilitation%20body%20has%20done%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20which%20is%20to%20temporarily%20re-home%20residents%20elsewhere%20while%20constructing%20low-cost%20housing%20on%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20land%20-%20and%20while%20commissioning%20private%20builders%20who%20profit%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20luxury%20apartments%20in%20a%20smaller%20portion%20of%20the%20space.%20Critics%20argue%20the%20new%20buildings%20will%20be%20claustrophobic%2C%20ugly%2C%20and%20leave%20inhabitants%20vulnerable%20to%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPlans%20involve%20constructing%2040-story%20towers%20and%20roughly%20tripling%20the%20size%20of%20tenement%20residences%20into%20apartments.%20Previous%20experience%20with%20affordable%20housing%20projects%20in%20Mumbai%20suggests%20the%20concerns%20should%20be%20taken%20seriously%2C%20with%20long%20delays%20and%20even%20incomplete%20work%20representing%20risks%20for%20current%20inhabitants.%20Moreover%2C%20many%20fear%20that%20the%20new%20buildings%20will%20incur%20significant%20maintenance%20costs%2C%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20push%20out%20those%20who%20have%20been%20living%20in%20the%20chawls%20for%20decades%2C%20benefiting%20from%20below-market%20rents%20that%20have%20statutory%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESuch%20development%20shifts%20Mumbai%20away%20from%20a%20place%20where%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20richest%20share%20space%20with%20some%20of%20the%20most%20destitute%20and%20where%20housing%20has%20a%20clear%20connection%20to%20the%20ground-level%20surrounding.%20Take%20for%20example%2C%20Lodha%20Trump%20Tower%20in%20Lower%20Parel%2C%20located%20barely%20a%20kilometer%20from%20Worli's%20BDD%20Chawls.%20Mumbai%20has%20long%20been%20a%20place%20where%20a%20blue-collar%20worker%20from%20the%20chawls%20might%20rub%20shoulders%20with%20a%20banker%20living%20at%20Lodha%20Trump%20Tower%20as%20both%20walk%20to%20the%20railway%20station%20for%20their%20commutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBombay%20has%20never%20had%20'tony'%20areas%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mustansir%20Dalvi%2C%20professor%20at%20the%20Sir%20J.J.%20College%20of%20Architecture%20in%20Mumbai.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20city%20has%20always%20had%20the%20very%20rich%20and%20very%20poor%20living%20almost%20side%20by%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20seem%20mistaken%20to%20mourn%20the%20departure%20of%20the%20chawls%20and%20the%20social%20mixing%20they%20made%20possible.%20Not%20only%20have%20their%20conditions%20deteriorated%2C%20they%20also%20now%20appear%20out%20of%20step%20with%20contemporary%20notions%20of%20nuclear%20families%20and%20individualistic%20ways%20of%20life.%20It%20is%20still%20worth%20remembering%20that%20their%20conditions%20fostered%20a%20way%20of%20life%20that%20provided%20substantial%20support%20for%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvolving%20into%20a%20uniquely%20Indian%20kind%20of%20living%20space%2C%20they%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20culture%20of%20the%20city%20in%20numerous%20intangible%20ways.%20How%20much%20of%20their%20vibrant%20community%20life%20survives%20as%20they%20are%20replaced%20with%20skyscrapers%20will%20determine%20whether%20the%20financial%20capital%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20populous%20country%20can%20sustain%20a%20remarkable%2C%20living%20thread%20with%20its%20early%20history.%20As%20this%20hangs%20in%20the%20balance%2C%20it's%20worth%20reflecting%20on%20what%20lessons%20they%20might%20still%20offer%20for%20Mumbai's%20future%20development%2C%20especially%20in%20terms%20of%20affordability%2C%20semi-public%20social%20spaces%20and%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698812160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-06%2Fmumbai-chawl_650x400_51496740371.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchawls-made-mumbai-city-of-dreams-to-be-replaced-by-skyscrapers-soon-4533707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20more%20than%20a%20century%2C%20the%20chawls%20of%20Mumbai%20have%20acted%20as%20one%20of%20the%20city's%20most%20important%20forms%20of%20affordable%20housing.The%20Large%20tenement%20complexes%20were%20built%20during%20Mumbai's%20industrial%20boom%20from%20the%201850s%20through%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%2020th%20century%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchawls-made-mumbai-city-of-dreams-to-be-replaced-by-skyscrapers-soon-4533707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchawls-made-mumbai-city-of-dreams-to-be-replaced-by-skyscrapers-soon-4533707%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchawls-made-mumbai-city-of-dreams-to-be-replaced-by-skyscrapers-soon-4533707%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22When%20Akshaye%20praised%20Aishwarya's%20beauty%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698812117000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104875393%2Cimgsize-36206.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthrowback-when-akshaye-khanna-admitted-he-couldnt-take-his-eyes-off-aishwarya-rai-called-her-sexiest-actor-in-bollywood%2Farticleshow%2F104875393.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104875393.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EAkshaye%20Khanna%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20with%20Aishwarya%20Rai%20in%20films%20like%20'Taal'%20and%20'Aa%20Ab%20Laut%20Chalen%2C'%20named%20her%20as%20the%20sexiest%20actress%20in%20Bollywood.%20He%20admitted%20to%20being%20unable%20to%20take%20his%20eyes%20off%20her%2C%20finding%20it%20embarrassing.%20While%20their%20films%20together%20didn't%20do%20well%20at%20the%20box%20office%2C%20their%20chemistry%20in%20'Taal'%20was%20appreciated.%20Aishwarya's%20latest%20film%20is%20'Ponniyin%20Selvan%202%2C'%20while%20Akshaye%20was%20last%20seen%20in%20'Drishyam%202.'%20They%20haven't%20worked%20together%20since%