0establishing%20a%20mechanism%20to%20track%20the%20volume%20and%20source%20of%20these%20imports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20from%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Sunil%20Barthwal%20was%20issued%20two%20weeks%20ago%20to%20address%20the%20misinformation%20about%20potential%20laptop%20import%20restrictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20laptops%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20there%20are%20no%20restrictions%20as%20such.%20We%20are%20only%20saying%20that%20somebody%20who%20is%20importing%20these%20laptops%20has%20to%20be%20under%20close%20watch%20so%20that%20we%20can%20look%20at%20these%20imports.%20It%20is%20basically%20monitoring%2C%20which%20we%20are%20doing.%20It%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20restrictions%20as%20such%2C%26quot%3B%20Commerce%20Secretary%20Sunil%20Barthwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flaptop-import-move-change-centre-delays-import-restrictions-on-laptops-tablets-till-october-31-4271044%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Import%20Curbs%20On%20Laptops%20Deferred.%20Companies%20Need%20To%20Secure%20License%20By...%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20remarks%20carry%20significance%20as%20the%20government%20had%20previously%20announced%20in%20August%20that%20products%20like%20laptops%2C%20tablets%2C%20and%20computers%20would%20require%20licensing%2C%20effective%20November%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EExplaining%20further%2C%20Director%20General%20of%20Foreign%20Trade%20(DGFT)%20Santosh%20Kumar%20Sarangi%20said%20there%20will%20be%20an%20import%20management%20system%2C%20which%20will%20come%20into%20place%20on%20November%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20the%20government%20imposed%20import%20restrictions%20on%20laptops%2C%20computers%20(including%20tablet%20computers)%2C%20microcomputers%2C%20large%20or%20mainframe%20computers%2C%20and%20certain%20data%20processing%20machines%20with%20a%20view%20to%20boosting%20domestic%20manufacturing%20and%20cutting%20imports%20from%20countries%20like%20China.%20Following%20this%20notification%2C%20the%20IT%20hardware%20industry%20raised%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20already%20has%20an%20import%20monitoring%20system%20for%20certain%20products%20like%20steel%2C%20coal%2C%20and%20paper.%20The%20licensing%20conditions%20on%20imports%20were%20put%20in%20place%20on%20the%20grounds%20of%20security%20and%20to%20spur%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20these%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20think-tank%20Global%20Trade%20Research%20Initiative%20(GTRI)%2C%20India%20is%20critically%20dependent%20on%20China%20for%20day-to-day%20use%20and%20industrial%20products%20like%20mobile%20phones%2C%20laptops%2C%20components%2C%20solar%20cell%20modules%2C%20and%20integrated%20circuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20taken%20several%20steps%20to%20boost%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20electronic%20items%2C%20such%20as%20rolling%20out%20the%20production-linked%20incentive%20scheme%20and%20increasing%20customs%20duties%20on%20the%20number%20of%20electronic%20components.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20imports%20about%20%247-8%20billion%20worth%20of%20these%20goods%20every%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20country%20has%20imported%20personal%20computers%2C%20including%20laptops%2C%20worth%20%245.33%20billion%20in%202022-23%2C%20as%20against%20%247.37%20billion%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EImports%20of%20certain%20data%20processing%20machines%20stood%20at%20%24553%20million%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%2C%20as%20against%20%24583.8%20million%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20imports%20of%20microcomputers%20and%20processors%20stood%20at%20%241.2%20million%20in%20the%20last%20fiscal%20year%2C%20compared%20to%20%242.08%20million%20in%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20the%20government%20approved%20the%20Production-Linked%20Incentive%20Scheme%202.0%20for%20IT%20Hardware%20with%20a%20budgetary%20outlay%20of%20%E2%82%B9%2017%2C000%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20PTI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698806520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5ooi8qj_laptop-tablet-generic_625x300_05_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomputer-import-tablet-import-laptop-pc-import-deadline-ends-heres-what-government-will-do-now-4533566%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20marks%20a%20significant%20shift%20from%20the%20government's%20previous%20decision%20to%20require%20licenses%20for%20importing%20these%20products.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomputer-import-tablet-import-laptop-pc-import-deadline-ends-heres-what-government-will-do-now-4533566%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomputer-import-tablet-import-laptop-pc-import-deadline-ends-heres-what-government-will-do-now-4533566%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcomputer-import-tablet-import-laptop-pc-import-deadline-ends-heres-what-government-will-do-now-4533566%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWe'll%20See%20Artificial%20General%20Intelligence%20In%20Our%20Lifetimes%26quot%3B%3A%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWelcoming%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20executive%20order%20seeking%20to%20reduce%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20has%20said%20India%20is%20on%20the%20same%20page%20and%20the%20%26quot%3Bconvergence%20of%20the%20leading%20tech%20nations%20of%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20around%20making%20user%20safety%20the%20primary%20objective%20for%20any%20tech%20policymaking%20is%20a%20good%20forward%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20information%20technology%20also%20allayed%20fears%20of%20people%20losing%20their%20jobs%20because%20of%20AI%2C%20but%20added%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20an%20emphasis%20on%20learning%20new%20skills.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERegulatory%20Approach%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20believes%20that%20-%20along%20the%20lines%20of%20the%20US%20order%20-%20%C2%A0developers%20who%20pose%20a%20potential%20security%20risk%20must%20share%20the%20results%20of%20safety%20tests%20with%20the%20government%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20all%2C%20I%20welcome%20what%20President%20Biden%20and%20the%20US%20government%20have%20done.%20This%20is%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20historic%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%2C%20when%20the%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20visited%20the%20US%2C%20where%20the%20US%20and%20India%20have%20agreed%20to%20collaborate%20in%20AI%20and%20in%20semiconductor%20and%20in%20high-performance%20computing%20and%20in%20quantum%20computing.%20So%20AI%20is%20certainly%20an%20area%20where%20India%20and%20the%20US%20are%20going%20to%20work%20very%20closely%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%20our%20basic%20principles%20in%20how%20we%20view%20technology%20in%20general%20and%20the%20internet%20in%20particular%20is%20similar%20because%20we%20have%20been%20saying%20for%20almost%2024%20months%20now%20that%20our%20policies%20and%20our%20approach%20to%20regulation%20are%20about%20safety%20and%20trust%20and%20accountability%2C%20safety%20and%20trust%20of%20our%20digital%20nagriks%20and%20accountability%20of%20all%20the%20platforms%20that%20serve%20our%20digital%20nagriks...%20And%20it%20is%20good%20to%20see%20that%20now%20the%20US%20is%20essentially%20talking%20about%20safety%20and%20trust%20and%20accountability%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20every%20country's%20approach%20may%20be%20a%20little%20different%2C%20the%20minister%20said%20India%20is%20proposing%20the%20creation%20of%20an%20overall%20framework%20of%20user%20harm%2C%20which%20is%20the%20reciprocal%20of%20safety%20and%20trust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20kinds%20of%20user%20harm%20are%20not%20permitted%20by%20any%20platform%2C%20whether%20that's%20an%20AI%20platform%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20consumer%20tech%20platform%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20social%20media%20platform%2C%20that%20we%20start%20regulating%20the%20Internet%20in%20general%2C%20and%20AI%20in%20particular%2C%20through%20the%20prism%20of%20the%20safety%20and%20trust%20of%20those%20who%20use%20it.%20AI%20is%20a%20technology%20that%20is%20going%20to%20enable%20us%20to%20do%20more%20with%20less.%20So%20do%20more%20good%20with%20less.%20We%20will%20certainly%20become%20a%20force%20multiplier%20and%20a%20kinetic%20enabler%20of%20a%20digital%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20the%20same%20principle%20applies%20to%20the%20bad%20and%20the%20harm%2C%20which%20is%20that%20AI%20will%20be%20able%20to%20amplify%20and%20compound%2C%20in%20very%20significant%20manners%2C%20the%20harm%20and%20the%20criminality%20elements%20of%20the%20internet%20as%20we%20know%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20warned.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20India%20will%20be%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20digital%20economies%20by%202025-26%20and%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20interest%20in%20helping%20AI%20being%20shaped%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20adds%20to%20the%20digital%20economy%20and%20does%20not%20cause%20harm%20and%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%20in%20ensuring%20that%20governments%20do%20not%20break%20the%20potential%20of%20AI%20by%20over-regulation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETimeline%20For%20Artificial%20General%20Intelligence%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20AI%20reaching%20a%20stage%20where%20it%20can%20think%20for%20itself%20and%20is%20getting%20to%20a%20stage%20where%20that%20represents%20a%20threat%2C%20Mr%20Chandrasekhar%20said%20artificial%20general%20intelligence%20(AGI)%20is%20something%20that%20people%20have%20spoken%20about%20for%20decades.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainly%2C%20we%20can%20argue%20that%2C%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20the%20intensity%20and%20the%20acceleration%20and%20the%20curve%20has%20become%20a%20lot%20more%20exponential%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20progress.%20But%20whether%20we%20will%20be%20there%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20whether%20we'll%20be%20there%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years...%20I'm%20certainly%20not%20a%20person%20who%20wants%20to%20predict%20the%20future%20of%20tech...%20but%20we%20can%20safely%20predict%20that%20in%20our%20lifetimes%20we%20will%20see%20AGI%2C%20we%20will%20see%20AI%20mimicking%20human%20behaviour%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20critical%20mass%20and%20an%20inflection%20point%20has%20been%20reached%20with%20the%20power%20of%20the%20GPUs%20(Graphics%20Processing%20Units)%20and%20the%20AI%20compute%20and%20the%20training%20models%20that%20have%20now%20evolved%20that%20we%20are%20able%20to%20train%20trillions%20of%20parameters%20and%20are%20starting%20to%20mimic%20close%20to%20inferential%20behaviour%20that%20human%20intelligence%20and%20human%20artificial%20intelligence%20of%20AGI%20represents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20A%20Threat%20To%20Jobs%2C%20An%20Opportunity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20people%20fearing%20that%20they%20will%20lose%20their%20jobs%20with%20the%20advent%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20%C2%A0the%20minister%20said%20such%20fears%20have%20dogged%20every%20major%20technological%20change.%20He%20pointed%20out%20that%20people%20had%20thought%20every%20retail%20showroom%20would%20shut%20down%20after%20e-commerce%20came%20to%20be%20widely%20adopted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Chandraskhar%20said%20that%20the%20disruption%20will%20not%20throw%20people%20out%20of%20work%20as%20much%20as%20it%20will%20force%20them%20to%20adapt.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20think%2C%20in%20our%20case%2C%20the%20opportunity%20for%20us%20is%20that%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20youngsters%20get%20the%20skills%20at%20the%20school%20and%20college%20levels%20that%20prepare%20them%20to%20be%20flexible%20and%20to%20be%20dynamic%20as%20these%20changes%20confront%20them.%20I%20think%20the%20days%20when%20you%20just%20get%20a%20degree%20after%20going%20to%20four%20years%20in%20college%20and%20then%20hoping%20and%20thinking%20that%20it%20will%20stand%20the%20course%20or%20test%20of%20time%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20life%20are%20pretty%20much%20behind.%20Not%20just%20in%20India%20but%20the%20whole%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStriking%20a%20positive%20note%2C%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20what%20this%20does%20is%20essentially%20create%20a%20lot%20more%20opportunities%2C%20but%20very%20different%20skill-intensive%20opportunities.%20There%20will%20be%20disruptions%20in%20the%20economic%20model%20and%20the%20market%20model%20as%20we%20know%20it...%20but%20that%20disruption%20is%20just%20normal.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20how%20humankind%20has%20progressed%20over%20the%20last%20several%20decades%20and%20centuries%20When%20the%20locomotive%20came%2C%20the%20bullet%20carts%20went%20out%20of%20action.%20When%20the%20PC%20came%2C%20the%20munshis%20went%20out%20of%20action.%20We%20must%20not%20fear%20it.%20We%20must%20embrace%20it.%20But%20we%20must%20certainly%20anticipate%20what%20it%20requires%20of%20us...%20to%20go%20with%20the%20change%20and%20write%20the%20change%20rather%20than%20be%20disrupted%20by%20the%20change.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeaponisation%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20every%20country%20will%20comply%20with%20AI%20standards%20and%20the%20potential%20weaponisation%20of%20AI%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20minis