e-threats-jewish-students-campus%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20U.S.%20Attorney's%20Office%2C%20Northern%20District%20of%20New%20York%2C%20prosecutors%20allege%20Dai%20was%20behind%20a%20series%20of%20threatening%20online%20posts%20targeting%20Jewish%20students%20at%20Cornell%2C%20including%20calling%20for%20the%20deaths%20of%20Jewish%20people%20and%20a%20threat%20that%20said%20%26quot%3Bgonna%20shoot%20up%20104%20west.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20104%20West%20is%20home%20to%20a%20dining%20hall%20that%20serves%20Kosher%20food%20and%20is%20next%20to%20the%20Center%20for%20Jewish%20Living%2C%20a%20student-run%20organization%20that%20supports%20the%20Jewish%20community%20on%20campus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20another%20post%2C%20Dai%20allegedly%20threatened%20to%20'stab'%20and%20'slit%20the%20throat'%20of%20any%20Jewish%20males%20he%20sees%20on%20campus%2C%20to%20rape%20and%20throw%20off%20a%20cliff%20any%20Jewish%20females%2C%20and%20to%20behead%20any%20Jewish%20babies%2C%26quot%3B%20prosecutors%20alleged%20in%20the%20statement.%20%26quot%3BIn%20that%20same%20post%2C%20Dai%20threatened%20to%20'bring%20an%20assault%20rifle%20to%20campus%20and%20shoot%20all%20you%20pig%20jews.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20charge%20filed%20against%20Dai%20%E2%80%94%20posting%20threats%20to%20kill%20or%20injure%20another%20using%20interstate%20communications%20%E2%80%94%20carries%20a%20maximum%20potential%20term%20of%20up%20to%20five%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20a%20fine%20of%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000%2C%20and%20a%20term%20of%20supervised%20release%20of%20up%20to%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDai%20is%20expected%20to%20make%20his%20initial%20appearance%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20federal%20court%20in%20Syracuse%2C%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20arrest%20comes%20as%20Cornell's%20campus%20was%20on%20high%20alert%20over%20the%20weekend.%20Some%20Jewish%20students%20opted%20to%20leave%20campus%20over%20the%20threats%20of%20danger%2C%20while%20others%20made%2