ney%2C%20head%20of%20US%20Army%20Futures%20Command%2C%20told%20reporters%20at%20the%20Association%20of%20the%20United%20States%20Army's%20annual%20conference%2C%20held%20this%20month%20in%20Washington%20DC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Army%20soldiers%20M777%20howitzer%20artillery%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653ff2ed96f7540cd06984cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20soldiers%20prepare%20a%20M777%20howitzer%20for%20fire%20missions%20at%20a%20training%20area%20in%20Germany%20in%20January%202020.%3Cp%3EUS%20Army%2FSpc.%20Rolyn%20Kropf%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukraine%20war%20has%20featured%20an%20array%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.nl%2Fthe-ukraine-war-has-often-been-a-grinding-artillery-battle-these-are-the-big-guns-being-sent-in-to-pound-russian-forces%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etowed%20and%20self-propelled%20artillery%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20calibers%20and%20manufactured%20by%20numerous%20nations.%20These%20include%20the%20US%20M109%2C%20Russian%202S19%2C%20and%20German%20PzH%202000%20self-propelled%20howitzers%2C%20and%20the%20US%20M777%2C%20Russian%202A65%2C%20and%20British%20L119%20towed%20guns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20are%20also%20using%20numerous%20weapons%20to%20hunt%20down%20the%20other's%20artillery%20batteries.%20These%20include%20counter-battery%20radars%20to%20locate%20hostile%20guns%20as%20soon%20as%20they%20fire%20and%20an%20armada%20of%20drones%20that%20hover%20over%20the%20battlefield%20constantly%2C%20waiting%20to%20pounce%20on%20unwary%20gunners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprecision-artillery-shells-aid-ukraine-in-artillery-battle-with-russia-2022-10%5C%22%3Eprecision-guided%20shells%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20the%20US-made%2C%20GPS-guided%20Excalibur%2C%20are%20also%20being%20used%20to%20destroy%20an%20enemy%20howitzer%20with%20one%20round%20instead%20of%20hoping%20for%20a%20lucky%20hit%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20unguided%20shells.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20spread%20and%20sophistication%20of%20anti-artillery%20systems%20will%20feed%20the%20long-running%20debate%20over%20the%20value%20of%20towed%20and%20self-propelled%20guns.%20For%20most%20of%20history%20%E2%80%94%20ever%20since%20cannon%20first%20appeared%20in%20the%20Middle%20Ages%20%E2%80%94%20the%20big%20guns%20were%20hauled%20by%20horses%20or%20oxen%2C%20which%20limited%20their%20mobility.%20By%20the%20time%20of%20the%20World%20Wars%2C%20trucks%20could%20more%20swiftly%20tow%20cannon%20around%20the%20battlefield%2C%20though%20the%20guns%20still%20required%20time%20to%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Army%20soldiers%20artillery%20World%20War%20II%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653ff2ec356802a56be7b315%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221404%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20soldiers%20use%20a%20tractor%20to%20pull%20a%20%26quot%3BLong%20Tom%26quot%3B%20artillery%20gun%20to%20the%20front%20in%20Sicily%20in%20September%201943.%3Cp%3ECORBIS%2FCorbis%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20World%20War%20II%20saw%20the%20debut%20of%20self-propelled%20howitzers%2C%20often%20mounted%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftank-afv.com%2Fww2%2FUS%2FM7_Priest.php%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econverted%20tank%20chassis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20tracked%20vehicles%20could%20not%20only%20keep%20up%20with%20tanks%20in%20cross-country%20movement%20but%20also%20shoot%2C%20rapidly%20relocate%2C%20and%20then%20shoot%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20nations%20especially%20tend%20to%20base%20their%20artillery%20arsenals%20on%20self-propelled%20guns%20that%20resemble%20lightly%20armored%20tanks.%20Those%20militaries%20often%20earmark%20towed%20cannons%20for%20airborne%20and%20amphibious%20forces%20that%20can't%20travel%20with%20heavy%20equipment%20or%20pass%20them%20off%20to%20less%20advanced%20allies%20that%20can't%20operate%20mechanized%20artillery.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20sides%20in%20the%20towed%20vs.%20self-propelled%20debate%20make%20strong%20arguments.%20Advocates%20of%20self-propelled%20howitzers%20point%20to%20their%20superior%20protection%20and%20their%20ability%20to%20rapidly%20displace%20after%20firing.%20Supporters%20of%20towed%20guns%20cite%20their%20lower%20cost%2C%20lighter%20weight%2C%20and%20improved%20setup%20times.%20(The%20US-made%20M777%20is%20reportedly%20able%20to%20displace%20and%20emplace%20within%20two%20to%20three%20minutes.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ukraine%20troops%20fire%20M777%20howitzer%20in%20Kharkiv%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6320cb5d89d2b3001894e1f2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkrainian%20troops%20fire%20an%20M777%20howitzer%20in%20the%20Kharkiv%20Region%20in%20July%202022.%3Cp%3EVyacheslav%20Madiyevskyy%2FUkrinform%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELogistically%2C%20towed%20cannon%20are%20less%20demanding.%20If%20a%20truck%20hauling%20a%20cannon%20breaks%20down%2C%20another%20truck%20can%20tow%20it.%20If%20the%20chassis%20of%20a%20self-propelled%20gun%20breaks%20down%2C%20the%20weapon%20is%20sidelined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sort%20of%20hybrid%20solution%20is%20truck-mounted%20howitzers%2C%20such%20as%20France's%20Caesar.%20These%20offer%20self-propelled%20mobility%20without%20the%20cost%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20mechanical%20complexity%2C%20though%20they%20also%20lack%20armored%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20future%2C%20another%20option%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20artillery%20that%20can%20be%20operated%20remotely%20or%20operate%2