oof%20glass%20for%20the%20vehicle%2C%20though%20that%20variant%20will%20pose%20a%20major%20usability%20tradeoff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20make%20anything%20bulletproof%20if%20you%20want%2C%20but%20the%20glass%20has%20to%20be%20very%20thick%20for%20be%20bulletproof%2C%20so%20it%20can't%20go%20up%20and%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20bulletproof%20windows%20will%20be%20immobile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20Rogan%20even%20tested%20out%20the%20Cybertruck's%20exterior%20by%20shooting%20an%20arrow%20at%20the%20vehicle's%20stainless%20steel%20body.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20the%20arrow%20appeared%20to%20partially%20break%20against%20the%20car's%20exterior%2C%20leaving%20a%20small%20dent%20in%20the%20side%20of%20the%20Cybertruck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221706%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Joe%20Rogan%20shot%20an%20arrow%20at%20the%20Cybertruck.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65416c7536d588dc55c7585d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22959%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJoe%20Rogan%20shot%20an%20arrow%20at%20the%20Cybertruck.%3Cp%3EThe%20Joe%20Rogan%20Experience%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20there%20will%20be%20three%20demonstrations%20to%20prove%20the%20Cybertruck%20is%20bulletproof%2C%20including%20shooting%20the%20vehicle%20with%20a%20Tommy%20gun%2C%20a%2045%20milimeter%20shotgun%2C%20and%20a%209%20milimeter%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrucks%20are%20supposed%20to%20be%20tough%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Musk%20first%20revealed%20the%20Cybertruck%20in%202019%20he%20attempted%20to%20demonstrate%20the%20vehicle's%20%26quot%3Barmour%20glass%26quot%3B%20windows%20by%20having%20Tesla's%20design%20boss%20throw%20a%20metal%20ball%20at%20the%20Cybertruck's%20window.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20glass%20immediately%20broke%20on%20contact%20with%20the%20metal%20ball.%20Musk%20later%20%3Ca%20