.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-debt-crisis-online-college-universities-class-providers-opms-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrand%20Canyon%20University%3C%2Fa%3E%20%2437.7%20million%20following%20a%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20investigation%20that%20accused%20the%20school%20of%20lying%20to%20over%207%2C500%20former%20and%20current%20students%20over%20the%20costs%20of%20its%20doctoral%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20department%20official%20told%20reporters%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20press%20call%20that%20this%20is%20the%20largest%20penalty%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20ever%20enforced%20on%20a%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGCU%20lied%20about%20the%20cost%20of%20its%20doctoral%20programs%20to%20attract%20students%20to%20enroll%2C%26quot%3B%20FSA%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20Richard%20Cordray%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BFSA%20takes%20its%20oversight%20responsibilities%20seriously.%20GCU's%20lies%20harmed%20students%2C%20broke%20their%20trust%2C%20and%20led%20to%20unexpectedly%20high%20levels%20of%20student%20debt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.ed.gov%2Fpolicy%2Fgen%2Fleg%2Ffoia%2Fgrand-canyon-university-10-31-23-redacted.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%2C%20GCU%20stated%20that%20its%20doctoral%20programs%20cost%20between%20%2440%2C000%20and%20%2449%2C000%2C%20when%20in%20reality%2C%20students%20ended%20up%20paying%20roughly%2025%25%20more%20than%20the%20school%20advertised.%20The%20Education%20Department%20said%20that%20in%20response%2C%20GCU%20pointed%20to%20the%20fine%20print%20in%20its%20enrollment%20agreements%20to%20justify%20the%20discrepancies%2C%20but%20the%20department%20said%20those%20disclosures%20are%20%26quot%3Binsufficient%20to%20cure%20the%20substantial%20misrepresentations%20regarding%20cost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGCU%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20Insider%20that%20it%20%26quot%3Bcategorically%20denies%20every%20accusation%20in%20the%20Department%20of%20Education's%20statement%20and%20will%20take%20all%20measures%20necessary%20to%20defend%20itself%20from%20these%20false%20accusations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Department's%20claims%20of%20wanting%20to%20protect%20students%20from%20'unexpectedly%20high%20levels%20of%20debt'%20at%20GCU%20are%20false%20given%20that%20our%20graduates%20incur%20less%20debt%20than%20the%20national%20average%2C%20and%20far%20less%20than%20other%20private%20universities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued.%20%26quot%3BRather%20than%20the%20Department%20protecting%20students%2C%20we%20are%20being%20forced%20to%20protect%20our%20students%20from%20this%20targeted%20and%20unwarranted%20government%20overreach.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGCU%20has%2020%20days%20to%20request%20a%20hearing%20on%20the%20fine%20or%20submit%20written%20material%20indicating%20why%20the%20fine%20should%20not%20be%20imposed.%20Along%20with%20the%20fine%2C%20the%20department%20is%20also%20enforcing%20specific%20conditions%20on%20the%20school%20to%20allow%20it%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Econtinue%20participating%20in%20federal%20student%20aid%20programs%2C%20including%20a%20requirement%20to%20inform%20students%20of%20the%20average%20total%20tuition%20and%20fees%20paid%20by%20graduates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20department%20official%20also%20noted%20to%20reporters%20on%20the%20press%20call%20that%20while%20this%20fine%20is%20an%20enforcement%20action%20against%20the%20school%2C%20borrowers%20who%20believe%20they%20were%20defrauded%20can%20also%20submit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-upholds-student-loan-debt-cancellation-defrauded-borrowers-settlement-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eborrower%20defense%20claims%20for%20student-debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20department%20has%20taken%20action%20numerous%20times%20over%20the%20past%20year%20to%20provide%20relief%20to%20borrowers%20it%2