0iPhone%20users%20of%20possible%20theft%20of%20their%20data%2C%20and%20communication%20and%20also%20the%20possible%20compromise%20of%20their%20camera%20and%20microphone.%20The%20nature%20of%20this%20attack%20has%20an%20uncanny%20resemblance%20to%20the%20Pegasus%20military-grade%20spyware%2C%20developed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20cybersecurity%20company%20NSO%20Group.%20This%20spyware%2C%20which%20NSO%20claims%20is%20only%20used%20to%20target%20terrorist%20and%20organised%20crime%20groups%2C%20was%20allegedly%20misused%20against%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20politicians%20and%20journalists%20from%20as%20early%20as%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202021%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20in%20collaboration%20with%2016%20other%20media%20organisations%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fproject-pegasus-list-of-names-uncovered-spyware-surveillance%5C%22%3Erevealed%20the%20names%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20people%2C%20including%20many%20Indians%2C%20who%20were%20either%20persons%20of%20interest%20or%20were%20forensically%20identified%20as%20targets%20of%20clients%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20investigation%20had%20prompted%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20three-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20led%20by%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20N.V.%20Ramana%2C%20to%20appoint%20an%20Expert%20Committee%20headed%20by%20Justice%20(Retired)%20R.V.%20Raveendran%20to%20look%20into%20the%20allegations%20in%20the%20Pegasus%20spyware%20case%2C%20%E2%80%9Ctaking%20into%20account%20the%20public%20importance%20and%20the%20alleged%20scope%20and%20nature%20of%20the%20large-scale%20violation%20of%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%20Interestingly%2C%20the%20government%20neither%20admitted%20nor%20denied%20the%20use%20of%20the%20malware.%20Finally%2C%20the%20committee%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20did%20not%20cooperate%20with%20the%20panel%2C%20concluded%20that%20while%20there%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpegasus-spyware-supreme-court-truth%5C%22%3Edefinite%20presence%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20malware%20on%20five%20handsets%20that%20it%20examined%2C%20there%20was%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cno%20conclusive%20evidence%20for%20the%20use%20of%20the%20NSO%20Group%E2%80%99s%20Pegasus%20spyware%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EApple%E2%80%99s%20latest%20alert%20has%20once%20again%20kickstarted%20the%20conversation%20that%20had%20died%20down%20following%20the%20expert%20committee%E2%80%99s%20report%20and%20the%20subsequent%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20on%20August%2025%2C%202022.%20But%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20alert%20where%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20has%20been%20explicitly%20alleged%20by%20a%20tech%20company.%20The%20language%20is%20identical%20to%20what%20the%20phone%20manufacturer%20has%20used%20on%20several%20occasions%20in%20the%20past%20to%20alert%20the%20victims%20of%20spyware%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20both%20Yahoo%20and%20Google%20have%20sent%20similar%20alerts%20in%20past%20years.%20In%20November%202019%2C%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20story%20about%20the%20use%20of%20the%20insidious%20spyware%20Pegasus%20in%20India%20broke%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fyahoo-email-snooping-partho-sarothi-ray%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20first%20reported%20about%20a%20message%20sent%20out%20by%20Yahoo%20to%20a%20user%20about%20the%20attack%20by%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment-backed%20actors%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20message%2C%20Yahoo%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20your%20Yahoo%20account%20may%20have%20been%20the%20target%20of%20government-backed%20actors%2C%20which%20means%20that%20they%20could%20gain%20access%20to%20the%20information%20in%20your%20account.%E2%80%9D%20Yahoo%2C%20however%2C%20had%20not%20clarified%20who%20this%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment-backed%20actor%E2%80%9D%20is%20or%20indeed%20what%20government%20they%20work%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Google%20too%2C%20that%20same%20year%2C%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Fgoogle-warning-india-users%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewarned%20up%20to%20500%20India-based%20targets%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20may%20have%20been%20the%20victims%20of%20a%20snooping%20attempt%20by%20%E2%80%9Cgovernment-backed%20actors%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fapple-responds-to-alerts-to-opposition-mps-read-full-statement-101698740136936.html%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20issued%20by%20Apple%20provided%20some%20clues%20about%20why%20tech%20companies%20do%20not%20provide%20additional%20information%20about%20the%20alleged%20attacks.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20unable%20to%20provide%20information%20about%20what%20causes%20us%20to%20issue%20threat%20notifications%2C%20as%20that%20may%20help%20state-sponsored%20attackers%20adapt%20their%20behaviour%20to%20evade%20detection%20in%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20US%20tech%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20a%20tech%20company%20puts%20out%20an%20alert%2C%20it%20is%20also%20taking%20a%20huge%20risk%20of%20alienating%20its%20service%20users.%20Every%20time%20such%20an%20alert%20is%20sent%20out%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20public%20furore%2C%20the%20government%20has%20opted%20to%20stay%20silent%2C%20respond%20in%20vague%20terms%20or%20accuse%20those%20seeking%20an%20independent%20probe%20into%20allegations%20of%20misuse%20of%20malware%20as%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fashwini-vaishnaw-parliament-pegasus-snooping-allegations%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eattempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmalign%20Indian%20democracy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20As%20the%20government%20continues%20to%20refuse%20to%20come%20out%20with%20a%20clear%20denial%20that%20it%20does%20not%20allow%20the%20misuse%20of%20spyware%2C%20probable%20victims%20of%20data%20theft%20and%20snooping%20have%20no%20scope%20for%20resolution.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20light%20of%20the%20latest%20Apple%20alert%2C%20Union%20minister%20for%20electronics%20and%20IT%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20was%20compelled%20to%20order%20a%20probe.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20government%20is%20concerned%20about%20this%20issue%20and%20it%20will%20get%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20it.%20We%20have%20already%20ordered%20%5Ban%5D%20investigation%20into%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnaw%20noted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698775811000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31232256%2Fpexels-o%25C4%259Fuzhan-%25C3%25B6nc%25C3%25BC-14168781.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fapple-tech-company-allege-government-role-spyware-misuse%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20potential%20nature%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20as%20described%20by%20Apple%2C%20has%20an%20uncanny%20resemblance%20to%20the%20Pegasus%20military-grade%20spyware%2C%20developed%20by%20the%20Israeli%20cybersecurity%20company%20NSO%20Group.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fapple-tech-company-allege-government-role-spyware-misuse%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22King%20says%20there%20is%20'no%20excuse'%20for%20'unjustifiable%20violence'%20of%20British%20colonial%20rule%20in%20Kenya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698774300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F1600x900%2Fskynews-king-charles-kenya_6343234.jpg%3F20231031173455%