d%20hundreds%20wounded%20in%20an%20Israeli%20air%20strike%20on%20a%20refugee%20camp%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20the%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20warned%20of%20a%20looming%20public%20health%20catastrophe.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20director%20of%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20Indonesian%20Hospital%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2023%2F10%2F31%2Fisrael-hamas-war-live-israeli-air-attacks-continue-across-gaza%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20more%20than%2050%20Palestinians%20were%20killed%20and%20150%20wounded%20in%20Israeli%20air%20strikes%20on%20the%20populated%20Jabalia%20refugee%20camp%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20refugee%20camp%20covers%20an%20area%20of%20only%201.4%20square%20kilometres%20but%20houses%20some%20116%2C000%20registered%20refugees.%20The%20Israeli%20military%20has%20repeatedly%20struck%20the%20camp%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%20that%20at%20least%208%2C525%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Israeli%20strikes%20since%20October%208%20and%20two-thirds%20of%20those%20killed%20are%20women%20and%20children.%20At%20least%203%2C542%20children%20and%202%2C187%20women%20were%20among%20the%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20spokesperson%20Ashraf%20Al-Qudra%20said%20130%20healthcare%20staff%20were%20killed%20and%2015%20hospitals%20are%20now%20out%20of%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUN%20secretary%20general%20Antonio%20Guterres%20said%20the%20escalation%20of%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20armed%20Palestinian%20groups%20will%20only%20increase%20the%20immense%20suffering%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20am%20deeply%20alarmed%20by%20the%20intensification%20of%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20and%20other%20Palestinian%20armed%20groups%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20too%20many%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20lives%20already%20lost%2C%20this%20escalation%20only%20increases%20the%20immense%20suffering%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%20(%40antonioguterres)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fantonioguterres%2Fstatus%2F1719390809462898957%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2031%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20WHO%20official%20told%20a%20press%20briefing%20in%20Geneva%20that%20people%20in%20Gaza%20are%20facing%20a%20looming%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20health%20catastrophe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20tightened%20its%20blockade%20on%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20home%20to%202.3%20million%20people%2C%20following%20the%20Hamas%20terror%20attacks%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20more%20than%20150%20trucks%20carrying%20humanitarian%20supplies%20have%20been%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20territory%20from%20Egypt%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%2C%20aid%20workers%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDamage%20to%20water%20and%20sanitation%20infrastructure%2C%20overcrowding%20and%20mass%20displacement%20are%20compounding%20an%20already%20dire%20humanitarian%20situation%20in%20the%20territory%2C%20they%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20WHO%20spokesperson%20said%20fuel%20was%20urgently%20needed%20to%20run%20generators%20at%20clinics%2C%20to%20treat%20water%20and%20for%20emergency%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698771622000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31221251%2FScreenshot-2023-10-31-at-10.12.04%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraeli-strike-jabalia-refugee-camp-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Gaza%20health%20ministry%20said%20that%20at%20least%208%2C525%20people%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20Is