er-jets-targeted-hamas-commander-in-deadly-strike-on-gaza-refugee-camp-12997286%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisrael-says-its-fighter-jets-targeted-hamas-commander-in-deadly-strike-on-gaza-refugee-camp-12997286%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Bowling%20Attack%2C%20Diverse%20and%20Deadly%2C%20Is%20Fuelling%20World%20Cup%20Run%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31194438%2FF9nnT1BasAA73q1.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Extra%20Cover%E2%80%99%20is%20veteran%20journalist%20Pradeep%20Magazine%E2%80%99s%20column%20on%20the%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20piece%20is%20as%20much%20a%20celebration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20(so%20far)%20invincible%20World%20Cup%20cricket%20team%2C%20as%20it%20is%20of%20its%20diversity.%20Never%20has%20an%20Indian%20team%20in%20my%20living%20memory%20or%20beyond%20that%2C%20been%20so%20representative%20of%20what%20India%20as%20a%20nation%20is.%20Unity%20in%20diversity%20may%20sound%20a%20trite%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20especially%20when%20we%20are%20living%20in%20divisive%20times%2C%20but%20it%20still%20best%20sums%20up%20a%20country%20which%20is%20a%20melting%20pot%20of%20different%20religions%20and%20castes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20may%20be%20screaming%20%E2%80%98Rohit%2C%20Rohit%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Kohli%2C%20Kohli%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20it%20is%20the%20team%E2%80%99s%20lethal%20bowling%20and%20the%20variety%20it%20has%20to%20offer%20that%20is%20leading%20India%E2%80%99s%20unstoppable%20march%20and%20makes%20them%20easily%20the%20most%20favoured%20team%20to%20win%20the%20World%20Cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20323px)%2085vw%2C%20323px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22323%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750.jpg%20976w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-244x300.jpg%20244w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31193029%2FIMG_2750-833x1024.jpg%20833w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22397%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20warriors%20%E2%80%93%20a%20Ramgarhia%20Sikh%2C%20two%20Muslims%2C%20one%20from%20an%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes)%20community%20and%20an%20upper%20caste%20person%20%E2%80%93%20are%20sending%20fear%20down%20the%20spine%20of%20the%20batsmen.%20They%20are%2C%20through%20their%20sheer%20skill%20and%20self-belief%2C%20entertaining%20thousands%20inside%20the%20stadium.%20The%20thunderous%2C%20cacophonic%20sounds%20that%20create%20a%20wave%20of%20support%20for%20the%20home%20team%20must%20sound%20like%20a%20death%20knell%20to%20the%20opposition%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20united%20flavour%20of%20Indian%20national%20identities%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%2C%20Kuldip%20Yadav%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20make%20an%20impregnable%20shield%2C%20and%2C%20probably%2C%20hold%20a%20lesson%20for%20our%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20something%20very%20strange%20and%20even%20intriguing%20about%20our%20nation%2C%20where%20caste%20and%20religion%20are%20the%20two%20most%20important%20markers%20of%20identity%20%E2%80%93%20yet%20we%20are%20shy%20to%20acknowledge%20it%20publicly.%20Those%20who%20control%20the%20levers%20of%20power%20would%20like%20us%20to%20believe%20caste%20does%20not%20matter%20but%20are%20proud%20of%20their%20upper%20caste%20lineage.%20Cricket%2C%20unlike%20many%20sports%20in%20India%2C%20has%20for%20long%20remained%20a%20preserve%20of%20the%20ruling%20elites.%20Most%20cricketers%20of%20the%20past%20may%20not%20have%20come%20from%20rich%20backgrounds%2C%20but%20were%20mostly%20city-bred%20middle-class%20Brahmins.%20Sure%2C%20Muslims%20and%20a%20few%20Sikhs%20or%20an%20odd%20Christian%20did%20break%20into%20the%20Indian%20team%2C%20but%20by%20and%20large%2C%20it%20has%20always%20been%20a%20struggle%20to%20find%20lower%20caste%20representation%20in%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20the%2080s%E2%80%99%20cricketing%20revolution%2C%20symbolised%20by%20India%20winning%20the%201983%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20the%20dynamic%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20a%20change%20started%20taking%20place.%20Kapil%20himself%20was%20from%20a%20non-cricketing%20centre%20like%20Chandigarh.%20When%20he%20lifted%20the%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20Lord%E2%80%99s%20balcony%2C%20Kapil%20ignited%20a%20billion%20dreams.%20For%20young%20kids%20in%20the%20lanes%20and%20bylanes%20of%20cities%20or%20village%20%3Cem%3Emaidans%3C%2Fem%3E%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20fantasy%20to%20aspire%20to%20play%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20late%2090s%20and%20finally%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%20boys%20from%20small%20towns%20were%20finding%20a%20place%20in%20the%20team%3A%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Dhoni%20being%20its%20best%20example%20and%20his%202011%20World%20Cup%20winning%20six%2C%20played%20with%20imperious%20nonchalance%2C%20remains%20an%20image%20no%20Indian%20can%20forget.%20This%20mix%20of%20big-city%20boys%20and%20small-town%20aspirants%2C%20backed%20by%20an%20expanding%20base%20and%20infrastructure%20for%20the%20game%2C%20has%20today%20propelled%20India%20to%20the%20number%20one%20team%20position%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20diversity%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20is%20obviously%20spreading%20and%20today%20an%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20no%20longer%20finds%20itself%20falling%20short%20of%20the%20religious%2Fcaste%20social%20matrix.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20would%20not%20be%20overstating%20the%20fact%20that%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20is%20a%20phenomenal%20bowler%2C%20whose%20unusual%20skills%20and%20intuitive%20understanding%20of%20his%20craft%20make%20him%20almost%20unplayable%20at%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20is%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20who%20follows%20the%20more%20conventional%20path.%20With%20the%20swerving%20ball%2C%20released%20after%20great%20dexterity%20from%20his%20cocked%20wrists%2C%20he%20creates%20magic%20to%20rattle%20the%20stumps.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMohammad%20Siraj%2C%20the%20least%20experienced%20of%20the%20trio%20but%20never%20short%20of%20effort%20and%20enthusiasm%2C%20keeps%20surprising%20the%20batsmen%20with%20his%20pace%20and%20movement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20these%20three%20were%20not%20a%20handful%2C%20the%20batsmen%20now%20have%20to%20deal%20with%20a%20different%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20foxy%2C%20wily%2C%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%2C%20aided%20by%20steely%20wrists%2C%20spins%20the%20ball%20both%20ways.%20His%20control%20of%20the%20pace%2C%20impeccable%20line%20and%20length%20leave%20the%20batsmen%20bewildered.%20Should%20he%20go%20forward%20or%20back%3F%20Will%20the%20ball%20turn%20away%2C%20come%20in%20or%20straighten%3F%20He%20is%20doomed%20in%20this%20web%20of%20confusion%20and%20uncertainty.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%20is%20exceptional.%20He%20is%20like%20a%20locomotive%20machine%2C%20which%20requires%20no%20greasing%20and%20can%20deliver%20ball%20after%20ball%20with%20variations%2C%20just%20minimum%20enough%20to%20fox%20the%20batsman.%20His%20control%20over%20his%20length%2C%20his%20athleticism%20and%20calm%20in%20nerve-wracking%20situations%20make%20him%20simply%20an%20indispensable%20member%20of%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20vital%20cog%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20diversity%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20team%3A%20a%20Dalit.%20What%20does%20it%20speak%20of%20a%20nation%20when%20a%20community%20that%20constitutes%20about%20a%20fifth%20of%20the%20population%20has%20no%20representation%20in%20its%20most%20popular%20sport%3F%20If%20even%20today%2C%20we%20have%20to%20go%20decades%20back%20and%20cite%20Palwankar%20Baloo%20as%20an%20example%20of%20a%20Dalit%20having%20played%20for%20India%2C%20it%20goes%20to%20show%20that%20we%20have%20failed%20the%20community.%20There%20is%20not%20enough%20space%2C%20access%20and%20encouragement%20to%20break%20through%20a%20systemic%20malaise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELet%20us%20for%20now%20celebrate%20the%20progress%20that%20has%20been%20made%20and%20hope%20that%20there%20is%20more%20in%20the%20future.%20As%20India%20inches%20closer%20towards%20its%20goal%20of%20winning%20the%20World%20Cup%2C%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Indian%20fans%20and%20the%20teeming%20crowds%20to%20realise%20diversity%20is%20a%20strength.%20It%20is%20to%20be%20celebrated%20and%20not%20drowned%20out%20by%20divisive%20slogans.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fpradeep-magazine%5C%22%3EPradeep%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20cricket%20writer%20and%20the%20author%20of%20two%20books%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20Not%20Quite%20Cricket%20%3Cem%3Eand%20the%20recently%20published%3C%2Fem%3E%20Not%20Just%20Cricket%2C%20A%20Reporter%E2%80%99s%20Journey%20Through%20Modern%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698762599000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F31194438%2FF9nnT1BasAA73q1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-bowling-attack-diverse-and-deadly-cricket-world-cup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cricket%2C%20unlike%20many%20sports%20in%20India%2C%20has%20for%20long%20remained%20a%20preserve%20of%20the%20ruling%20elites.%20But%20that%20has%20changed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A30%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsport%2Findia-bowling-attack-diverse-and-deadly-cricket-world-cup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Initiative%20Is%20Helping%204%20Lakh%20Girls%20in%2022%20States%20Break%20Barriers%20Through%20Sport%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Vidya%20Tamkhane%20was%20afraid%20to%20even%20step%20out%20of%20her%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20she%20was%20in%20Class%2010%20back%20in%202013%2C%20her%20brother%20took%20her%20to%20the%20playground%20and%20introduced%20her%20to%20kabaddi.%20She%20resisted%20participating%20at%20first%2C%20but%20he%20encouraged%20her%20to%20play.%20It%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20long%20before%20she%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20game%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20and%20the%20trajectory%20of%20her%20life%20changed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20simply%20accepting%20that%20she%20would%20get%20married%20when%20she%20reached%20a%20certain%20age%2C%20she%20became%20determined%20to%20make%20her%20own%20decisions.%20Last%20year%20in%202022%2C%20a%20few%20years%20after%20she%20got%20her%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20she%20interviewed%20with%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%20and%20was%20hired%20as%20a%20kabaddi%20coach%20in%20Chandrapur%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%5Btraditional%5D%20thinking%20is%20that%20boys%20should%20work%20because%20they%20have%20a%20family%20to%20feed%2C%20while%20girls%20are%20expected%20to%20get%20a%20good-looking%20husband%20with%20a%20government%20job.%20But%20my%20brother%20changed%20this%20outlook%20and%20supported%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vidya%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20job%20with%20Magic%20Bus%20inspired%20her%20to%20venture%20even%20further%20outside%20her%20comfort%20zone.%20She%20acquired%20the%20skills%20to%20effectively%20communicate%20with%20school%20principals%20about%20the%20value%20she%20gained%20from%20the%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20programmes%20of%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20and%20to%20persuade%20parents%20to%20enroll%20their%20daughters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPermission%20from%20parents%20is%20very%20difficult%20at%20times%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20feel%20%5Bit%20is%5D%20unsafe.%20It%20was%20very%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20win%20their%20trust%2C%20but%20I%20did%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidya%20was%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F322281%2Fbengaluru-duo-uses-sports-to-help-rural-girls-study-in-school-sportz-village%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esix%20female%20kabaddi%20coaches%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20similar%20backgrounds%20and%20ages%20(between%2023%20and%2025)%20who%20joined%20Magic%20Bus%20around%20the%20same%20time.%20The%20other%20coaches%20were%20Komal%20Pachare%2C%20Nilam%20Verma%2C%20Shital%20Borkar%2C%20Poornima%20Chandekar%20and%20Reema%20Khushwah%2C%20who%20shared%20a%20common%20goal%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F145074%2Flibrary-books-ruchi-dhona-children-education%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eto%20empower%20girls%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20sports%2C%20just%20as%20they%20were.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20are%20part%20of%20Magic%20Bus%E2%80%99%20School%20Completion%20and%20Livelihood%20Enablement%20Programme%20in%20Chandrapur.%20The%20purpose%20of%20the%20programme%20is%20to%20train%20teachers%20to%20deliver%20life%20skills%20education%20to%20adolescents%20from%20Class%206%20to%20Class%2010%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20government.%20Operating%20in%20Chandrapur%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20success%2C%20leading%20to%20Magic%20Bus%20initiating%20a%20partnership%20with%20the%20government%20to%20further%20expand%20their%20impact.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%2C%20founded%20by%20Matthew%20Spacie%20back%20in%201999%2C%20has%20impacted%20the%20lives%20of%20more%20than%20one%20million%20adolescents%20over%20the%20past%20two-plus%20decades.%20At%20present%203%2C94%2C206%20adolescents%20are%20enrolled%20in%20their%20programmes%20across%202%2C770%20schools.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20initial%20days%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAbout%2030%20years%20ago%2C%20when%20I%20arrived%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20ignore%20the%20stark%20contrast%20in%20living%20conditions%20within%20the%20city.%20On%20one%20side%2C%20there%20was%20a%20sizable%20middle-class%20population%2C%20living%20fairly%20ordinary%20lives.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20there%20was%20a%20parallel%20reality%20of%20people%20living%20in%20poor%20conditions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20outsider%2C%20this%20divide%20deeply%20affected%20me%2C%20compelling%20me%20to%20respond%20in%20some%20way.%20However%2C%20there%20was%20a%20personal%20connection%20that%20played%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20shaping%20my%20vision%20for%20Magic%20Bus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20girls%20playing%20football%20in%20their%20campus.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F8_11zon-1698734921-96x96.jpeg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333294%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESchool%20girls%20playing%20football%20on%20their%20campus.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESports%20for%20development%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation%20is%20a%20pioneer%20in%20the%20life%20skills%20education%20and%20skilling%20sector%20in%20India.%20Their%20mission%2C%20as%20Matthew%20states%2C%20has%20always%20been%20to%20help%20young%20people.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20started%20Magic%20Bus%2C%20our%20aim%20was%20to%20help%20young%20people%20thrive%20and%20find%20happiness%20and%20success.%20We%20took%20them%20on%20mountain%20trips%20and%20engaged%20in%20various%20activities%20to%20boost%20their%20resilience%20and%20happiness.%20Our%20community-based%20mentors%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%2C%20serving%20as%20role%20models%20who%20had%20conquered%20similar%20challenges.%20For%20me%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20mentors%20became%20evident%20early%20on.%20Within%20five%20years%2C%20our%20approach%20transformed%20from%20me%20playing%20rugby%20with%20young%20men%20at%20the%20Gymkhana%20to%20engaging%2010%2C000%20adolescents%20and%20young%20people%20across%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20life-changing%20programme%20led%20by%20mentors%20from%20their%20own%20communities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F317722%2Fmumbai-entrepreneurs-start-marketplace-for-ngo-products-jhappi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20organisation%20%3C%2Fa%3Eimplements%20a%20sports%20and%20activity-based%20life-skills%20programme%20with%20the%20goal%20to%20equip%20adolescents%20with%20essential%20life%20skills%20and%20facilitate%20a%20smoother%20transition%20from%20school%20to%20the%20workforce.%20It%20operates%20in%2024%20states%20across%2072%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F274165%2Ftop-inspiring-indian-villages-sustainable-development%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edistricts%20in%20India%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMagic%20Bus%20has%20played%20a%20pioneering%20role%20in%20introducing%20sports-for-development%20and%20life%20skills%20education%20in%20India%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%20%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20empower%20individuals%20to%20acquire%20essential%20life%20skills%20through%20sports.%20By%20gathering%20on%20the%20playground%2C%20we%20especially%20empower%20girls%20to%20assert%20their%20presence%20in%20a%20domain%20traditionally%20reserved%20for%20boys.%20We%20aim%20to%20challenge%20gender%20stereotypes%2C%20encouraging%20girls%20to%20break%20barriers%20while%20fostering%20equal%20participation%20from%20boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jayant%20Rastogi%2C%20Global%20CEO%2C%20Magic%20Bus%20India%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%20shows%20that%20adolescents%20in%20its%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.magicbus.org%2Fuploads%2Fpdf%2FMB_Impact%2520Report%252022-23.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20programmes%20improved%20their%20school%20regularity%20by%2021.8%25%2C%20a%2031%25%20increase%20in%20perceived%20self-efficacy%2C%20and%20a%2034.7%25%20boost%20in%20resilience.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22School%20boys%20being%20given%20a%20proper%20coaching%20for%20Cricket.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F5_11zon-1698734990-76