20case%20and%20was%20facing%20trial%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Kishtwar%20District%20Information%20Officer%20(DIO)%20Kuldeep%20Kumar%2C%20who%20had%20issued%20the%20ban%20order%20on%20Monday%20(October%2030)%2C%20issued%20a%20fresh%20order%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20saying%20that%20the%20previous%20one%20would%20be%20kept%20in%20abeyance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumar%2C%20a%20Kashmir%20Administrative%20Service%20officer%2C%20had%20on%20Monday%20ordered%20a%20blanket%20ban%20on%20the%20journalist%2C%20Anshuman%20Rathore%2C%20who%20works%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Alert%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20web-portal%20registered%20with%20the%20Registrar%20of%20Newspapers%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECiting%20a%20police%20case%20filed%20under%20sections%20451%20(house%20trespass)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20in%202019%20against%20Rathore%20at%20the%20Kishtwar%20police%20station%2C%20the%20DIO%20stated%20in%20his%20order%20that%20%E2%80%9Ca%20complete%20ban%E2%80%9D%20has%20been%20imposed%20on%20the%20reporter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20what%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20official%20overreach%2C%20the%20ban%20order%20%E2%80%93%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%93%20said%20that%20the%20reporter%2C%20who%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20convicted%20in%20the%20case%2C%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20perform%20his%20professional%20duties%20%E2%80%9Cuntil%20such%20time%20as%20he%20receives%20exoneration%20from%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20court%20of%20law%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20order%20on%20October%2027%2C%202023%2C%20the%20DIO%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Information%20and%20Public%20Relations%2C%20the%20official%20PR%20wing%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20administration%2C%20had%20asked%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Alert%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0to%20submit%20the%20reporters%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Ccharacter%20certificate%E2%80%9D%20in%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20organisation%20approached%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20for%20information%20on%20the%20reporter.%20According%20to%20a%20note%20signed%20by%20Kishtwar%E2%80%99s%20superintendent%20of%20police%2C%20the%20reporter%20was%20%E2%80%9Cfound%20involved%20in%20the%20case%20FIR%20No.%20256%2F2019%20u%2Fs%20451%2F506%20IPC%20(Indian%20Penal%20Code).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20challan%20of%20the%20case%20was%20produced%20in%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20court%20of%20law%20vide%20challan%20No%20233%2F2019%20Dated%3A%2009-11-2020.%20However%2C%20the%20instant%20case%20is%20still%20under%20trial%2Fsubjudice%20before%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20court%20of%20law%20and%20is%20not%20convicted%20so%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20note%20dated%20October%2019%2C%202023%2C%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fnewsclick-lessons-from-the-kashmir-template%5C%22%3ENewsClick%3A%20Lessons%20from%20the%20Kashmir%20Template%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20an%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Kishtwar%20district%20administration%20on%20August%2028%2C%202023%20had%20banned%20Azhar%20Ali%20Butt%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kijai%20in%20Kishtwar%E2%80%99s%20Padder%20tehsil%2C%20from%20working%20as%20a%20reporter%2C%20terming%20him%20a%20threat%20to%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20peace%20and%20tranquility%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EButt%2C%20who%20worked%20as%20a%20freelance%20reporter%20with%20local%20news%20outlets%2C%20was%20booked%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20in%20a%20case%20filed%20for%20kidnapping%20and%20criminal%20conspiracy%20at%20the%20Kishtwar%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20%E2%80%9Cserious%20adverse%20report%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%2C%20the%20DC%20had%20issued%20a%20show-cause%20notice%20to%20Butt%2C%20asking%20%E2%80%9Cwhy%20he%20may%20not%20be%20banned%20from%20any%20media%20reporting%20in%20the%20district%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20Butt%E2%80%99s%20reply%20to%20the%20notice%20was%20found%20%E2%80%9Cunsatisfactory%2C%20evasive%20and%20totally%20incomplete%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20naming%20Butt%2C%20the%20official%20order%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Csome%20media%20persons%E2%80%9D%20working%20in%20the%20district%20were%20%E2%80%9Cindulging%E2%80%A6%20in%20peddling%20fake%20news%20and%20maligning%20the%20image%20of%20government%20as%20well%20as%20creating%20hindrance%20in%20the%20smooth%20run%20of%20government%20works.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20district%20administration%20official%20said%20that%20Butt%20has%20been%20%E2%80%9Cdesignated%20as%20an%20overground%20worker%E2%80%9D%20of%20militants%20by%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20police.%20Invoking%20section%20144%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20(CrPC)%2C%20the%20DC%20had%20ordered%20Kishtwar%E2%80%99s%20senior%20superintendent%20of%20police%20to%20implement%20the%20ban%20on%20Butt%20for%20two%20months%C2%A0%E2%80%9Cin%20letter%20and%20spirit%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20said%20tainted%20media%20person%20is%20allowed%20to%20operate%20unchecked%2C%20it%20may%20be%20detrimental%20to%20public%20peace%20and%20tranquility%20and%20this%20also%20vitiates%20the%20peaceful%20atmosphere%20in%20the%20district%20%5Bsic%5D.%20Any%20deviation%20of%20this%20order%20shall%20invite%20punitive%20action%20under%20rules%20read%20with%20Section%20188%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20against%20the%20violator%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20DC%20said%20in%20the%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ban%20on%20the%20journalist%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Alert%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20has%20more%20than%2087%2C000%20followers%20on%20Facebook%2C%20has%20caused%20a%20fresh%20stir%20among%20local%20journalists%20in%20Kishtwar%2C%20who%20are%20questioning%20the%20administration%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20arbitrary%20use%20of%20rules%20and%20laws%20against%20members%20of%20their%20fraternity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20official%20survey%20puts%20the%20number%20of%20registered%20journalists%20in%20Kishtwar%20at%2047.%20According%20to%20sources%2C%20several%20journalists%20working%20in%20the%20hilly%20district%2C%20which%20falls%20in%20the%20Jammu%20division%2C%20have%20criminal%20cases%20filed%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20barring%20Rathore%20and%20Butt%2C%20none%20of%20them%20have%20been%20stopped%20from%20carrying%20out%20their%20professional%20duties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20legal%20experts%2C%20there%20is%20no%20law%20or%20rule%20that%20can%20bar%20a%20journalist%20or%20any%20other%20professional%20from%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties%20if%20they%20are%20booked%20in%20a%20police%20case%20and%20when%20the%20case%20is%20in%20the%20trial%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20cases%20against%20Rathore%20and%20Butt%20too%20are%20also%20undergoing%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20media%20owners%20should%20check%20the%20background%20of%20people%20before%20hiring%20them%20as%20reporters%20and%20photojournalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Imran%20Shah%2C%20a%20senior%20journalist%20in%20Kishwar%20who%20freelances%20with%20local%20and%20national%20media%20organisations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20proliferation%20of%20social%20media%20journalists%2C%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20professional%20degrees%2C%20has%20brought%20a%20bad%20name%20to%20journalism.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20administration%20to%20recognise%20only%20those%20journalists%20who%20come%20from%20%5Ba%5D%20journalism%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20in%20August%202019%2C%20press%20freedom%20has%20suffered%20a%20blow%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20at%20least%20five%20journalists%20incarcerated%20in%20the%20Union%20Territory%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Firfan-mehraj-kashmir-journalist-nia-arrest%5C%22%3Eterrorism%20and%20other%20charges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Several%20independent%20organisations%20that%20support%20press%20freedom%20across%20the%20globe%20have%20called%20upon%20the%20government%20of%20India%20to%20release%20these%20journalists%20unconditionally.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFree%20speech%20activists%20allege%20that%20press%20freedom%20has%20deteriorated%20over%20these%20years%20and%20the%20region%20has%20become%20a%20difficult%20place%20for%20journalists.%20Several%20journalists%20have%20been%20detained%20by%20security%20agencies%20in%20connection%20with%20their%20work%20while%20some%20Kashmiri%20journalists%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fsanna-irshad-mattoo-travel-pulitzer-usa-cpj%5C%22%3Eprevented%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20leaving%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20article%20was%20first%20published%20before%20the%20order%20banning%20Anshuman%20Rathore%20was%20withdrawn.%20The%20headline%20and%20text%20were%20updated%20subsequently.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698760820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07112943%2FScreenshot-2023-09-07-at-11.28.4.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjk-government-bans-journalist-anshuman-rathore-the-alert%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22According%20to%20legal%20experts%2C%20there%20is%20no%20law%20or%20rule%20that%20can%20bar%20a%20journalist%20or%20any%20other%20professional%20from%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties%20if%20they%20are%20booked%20in%20a%20police%20case%20and%20when%20the%20case%20is%20in%20the%20trial%20stage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fjk-government-bans-journalist-anshuman-rathore-the-alert%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mankind%20Pharma%20Q2%20results%3A%20Consolidated%20net%20profit%20rises%2021%25%20to%20Rs%20511%20cr%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698760482000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fb