ou%20can%20give%20me%20a%20few%20specific%20answers.%20Do%20you%20have%20things%20like%20anesthesia%20and%20oxygen%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20workable%20operating%20theaters%20or%20is%20all%20of%20that%20shut%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20some%20hospitals%2C%20they%20still%20have%20some%20anesthesia%2C%20especially%20for%20operations.%20B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eut%20for%20milder%20operations%2C%20they%20do%20it%20without%20anesthesia%2C%20unfortunately.%20Because%20there%20is%20too%20much%20pressure%20and%20there%20are%20no%20available%20devices%2C%20no%20available%20medicines%20to%20care%20for%20patients%20in%20the%20corridors.%20This%20is%20one%20thing.%20In%20other%20hospitals%2C%20they%20run%20out%20of%20sutures%20to%20close%20wounds%20because%20Israelis%20are%20using%20these%20kind%20of%20sophisticated%20weapons%20that%20causes%20hundreds%20of%20cut-wounds%20in%20the%20body%20just%20like%20cutting%20the%20bodies%20into%20pieces%2C%20which%20consumes%20all%20the%20suture%20and%20causes%20severe%20burns.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20so%20many%20cases%20and%20also%20was%20told%20by%20many%20of%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Esenior%20friends%20who%20work%20with%20burns%20that%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20they%20see%20such%20kinds%20of%20burns%20and%20damage%20to%20the%20skin.%20The%20skin%20is%20cut%20into%20pieces%20just%20like%20you%20cut%20it%20with%20a%20knife%20and%20burned%20completely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20they%20using%20phosphorus%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20any%20signs%20of%20phosphorus%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20using%20phosphorus%20and%20there%20are%20so%20many%20witnesses.%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20it%20for%20myself.%20I%20cannot%20confirm%20it%20myself%20but%20we%20have%20so%20many%20witnesses%20and%20so%20many%20doctors%20who%20confirm%20that%20they%20have%20dealt%20with%20cases%20of%20white%20phosphorus.%20Actually%2C%20to%20be%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ehonest%2C%20in%202009%20I%20published%20a%20paper%20in%20the%20Cochrane%20Library%2C%20talking%20about%20phosphorus%20and%20the%20injuries%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20with%20some%20of%20the%20patients%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20description%20that%20we%20have%20seen%20in%202009%20and%202012.%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENow%2C%20I%20can%20see%20that%20at%20the%20moment%20you%20have%20electricity%20but%20how%20often%20does%20Shifa%20Hospital%20have%20electricity%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20do%20you%20have%20clean%20water%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOkay%2C%20Shifa%20Hospital%20has%20no%20electricity%2C%20and%20now%20they%20are%20running%20on%20generators.%20Unfortunately%2C%20within%2024%20hours%20or%2040-48%20hours%2C%20electricity%20will%20be%20shut%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Edown%20and%20no%20more%20patients%20will%20be%20admitted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnd%20what%20about%20water%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20clean%20water%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlso%20no%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20we%20are%20drinking.%20This%20is%20actually%20a%20point%20I%20wanted%20to%20raise.%20Yes%2C%20we%20have%207%2C000%20patients%20who%20were%20killed%2C%207%2C000%20victims%20who%20were%20murdered%20and%2020%2C000%20people%20who%20were%20injured%20with%20their%20kids%20and%20their%20families.%20But%20we%20have%20300%2C000%20Palestinians%20who%20are%20dying%20in%20silence%20because%20they%20suffer%20from%20chronic%20illnesses%20and%20need%20their%20care.%20But%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethey%E2%80%99re%20not%20receiving%20it%20because%20of%20the%20inability%20to%20access%20hospital%20care%20in%20the%20primary%20health%20care%20centers.%20Inability%20to%20come%20to%20hospitals%20in%20the%20main%20hospitals%2C%20inability%20to%20commute%20because%20there%20are%20no%20cars%20and%20everybody%20is%20scared%20for%20their%20life.%20This%20is%20one%20thing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%