%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20third%20thing%20is%20that%20cancer%20patients%20who%20need%20this%20chemotherapy%20and%20radiotherapy%20are%20not%20receiving%20it.%20We%20have%2011%2C000%20patients%20with%20adrenal%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eneeds%20who%20need%2C%20sorry%2C%201%2C200%20patients%20who%20need%20regular%20renal%20dialysis%20and%20they%20are%20not%20receiving%20it%20regularly.%20So%20this%20poses%20a%20danger%20to%20their%20lives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETell%20me%20you%20said%20in%2024%20hours%2C%20the%20fuel%20at%20Shifa%20Hospital%20will%20stop.%20What%20then%20will%20happen%20to%20babies%20in%20incubators%3F%C2%A0%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20people%20on%20ventilators%3F%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20people%20who%20need%20dialysis%2C%20are%20they%20all%20destined%20to%20die%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMany%20of%20them%20will%20die.%20Fortunately%2C%20maybe%20five%20years%20ago%2C%20they%20installed%20on%20top%20of%20ICUs%2C%20some%20solar%20panels.%20These%20solar%20panels%20can%20save%20some%20patients%20who%20are%20in%20ventilators%20but%20patients%20who%20need%20who%20needed%20renal%20dialysis%2C%20blood%20transfusion%20like%20sickle%20cell%20anemia%20like%20patients%2C%20who%20suffer%20from%20blood%20disorders%2C%20patients%20who%20need%20plasmapheresis%20for%20any%20neurological%20disease%2C%20like%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20for%20neurological%20disease%2C%20like%20patients%20who%20have%20sickle%20cell%20anemia%20and%20patients%20who%20suffer%20from%20other%20diseases%2C%20they%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20receive%20any%20treatments%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20power.%20Not%20only%20that%20in%20Gaza%2C%20they%20have%20I%20think%20two%20main%20oxygen%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Estations%20which%20are%20running%20on%20power.%20Without%20electricity%2C%20those%20oxygen%20stations%20will%20stop%20and%20many%20patients%20will%20be%20at%20risk%20of%20death%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20oxygen.%C2%A0%3C%2Fs