0and%20with%20so%20many%20diverse%20sets%20of%20peoples%20and%20interests%20in%20such%20harmony%2C%20and%20brought%20about%20such%20remarkable%20results.%20And%20of%20course%20who%20can%20forget%20the%20power%20of%20her%20pen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRazaKazmi17%2Fstatus%2F1710262197698310376%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaza%20Kazmi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Society%20of%20India%20(WPSI)%2FFacebook%20and%20Kipling%20Camp%2FFacebook)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698676639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333222%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%204%20October%2C%202023%2C%20India%20mourned%20the%20loss%20of%20Anne%20Wright%2C%20a%20pioneering%20conservationist%20who%20dedicated%20over%20five%20decades%20to%20protecting%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20wildlife.%20Wildlife%20historian%20Raza%20Kazmi%20highlights%20Anne%E2%80%99s%20significant%20contributions%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Act%2C%20Project%20Tiger%2C%20and%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Palamau%20Tiger%20Reserve.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333222%2Fanne-wright-conservationist-wildlife-protection-act-reserves-project-tiger-legacy-raza-kazmi%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Soft%20Power!%20Meet%20the%20%E2%80%98Viral%E2%80%99%20Japanese%20Men%20Serving%20Authentic%20Idli-Dosa%20in%20Kyoto%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAsk%20Prasanna%20Karthik%2C%20a%20Fulbright%20Program%20Fellow%2C%20about%20where%20he%E2%80%99s%20tasted%20the%20best%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.co